Screen Open 0,640,512,16,$8004
Curs Off : Flash Off : Cls 0
'
While Mouse Key<>1 : Wend 
Gr Writing 2
X0=X Screen(X Mouse)
Y0=Y Screen(Y Mouse)
While Mouse Key=1
   X1=X Screen(X Mouse)
   Y1=Y Screen(Y Mouse)
   DIST=Max(1,Wb Distance(X0,Y0 To X1,Y1))
   Ellipse X0,Y0,DIST,DIST
   Ellipse X0,Y0,DIST,DIST
Wend 
Gr Writing 1
'
Ellipse X0,Y0,DIST,DIST
